I give all my service to You,
I give all my service to You.
No matter the cost or what others do
I give all my service to You.

 I give all my future to You,
I give all my future to You.
No matter the cost or what others do
I give all my future to You.

I give all my family to You,
I give all my family to You.
No matter the cost or what others do
I give all my family to You.

I give all my worship to You,
I give all my worship to You.
No matter the cost or what others do
I give all my worship to You.

